	1. adding dynamic price, need to use type = number, store as string so it will preserve what it looks like
    min is the min and step is how much we can increase as step
        
        <div class="form-group">
                    <input class="form-control" type="number" name="price" placeholder="price" min = "0.01" step = "0.5">
                </div>


